WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.230
Ready. Hey, good morning family. Praise

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:06.550
the Lord. Thank you for joining us again

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.870
today. We're excited to be here. We have

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:10.870
some things on our heart to pray about. There

00:00:10.870 --> 00:00:10.880
are

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:12.870
so many of you

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:14.789
already here is what I want

00:00:14.799 --> 00:00:17.029
to say, but we're excited to see you

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:20.310
all. We went to a Billy Burke

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:22.710
healing service this

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:24.390
week. That's where we were. If everybody

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.390
wanted to know, they're like, "How come

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:27.830
you're not posting videos?"Well, we're

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:30.630
getting refreshed. And we went down to

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:32.950
Fort Worth to see Billy Burke,

00:00:32.960 --> 00:00:36.549
and it was wonderful. You know, we

00:00:36.559 --> 00:00:39.510
had great expectations. We did. I told

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:41.510
her, "Man, I cannot wait

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:44.709
to go."The first night when we went,

00:00:44.719 --> 00:00:47.190
we saw so many of you all. I

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:48.709
mean, there were so many people that

00:00:48.709 --> 00:00:48.719
came

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:51.990
from all over the United States

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.150
to say hello to us and come to the

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:56.389
service and everything. So, you know,

00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:58.630
with me and Diana, I told her, I said,

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:00.470
"I'm not used to being in public and

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.549
people knowing who I am,

00:01:02.559 --> 00:01:04.149
especially in a church that's

00:01:04.149 --> 00:01:04.159
that

00:01:04.159 --> 00:01:07.910
big."Everybody

00:01:07.910 --> 00:01:07.920
came

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:09.910
up trying to introduce

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.550
themselves. I'm a person who

00:01:12.550 --> 00:01:12.560
is

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:14.950
already discerning; I'm trying to

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:17.510
see if you're a friend or a foe.

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:19.910
Are you here to be nice to me,

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.670
or are you going to come against

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:23.670
me? So I'm looking at people's

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:26.630
eyes. When there are that

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:28.230
many coming, and it's that much of a

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:29.749
flood, and I'm having that much of a

00:01:29.759 --> 00:01:32.069
download trying to

00:01:32.069 --> 00:01:32.079
find—I

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:33.270
told Braden, "That was really

00:01:33.270 --> 00:01:33.280
awkward,"because

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:35.429
I'm not used to that.

00:01:35.439 --> 00:01:37.109
Trying to shake everybody's hand and

00:01:37.119 --> 00:01:39.190
discern what's going on

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.670
with them, I told Diana,

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.270
"I'm going to have to practice a

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:44.789
lot because I'm not used to

00:01:44.789 --> 00:01:44.799
it."We're

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:47.190
hermits, y'all. We stay at home

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:49.190
a lot because of our daughter. You know,

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.350
she has special needs she's overcoming,

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.749
so I'm not used to going out and

00:01:53.759 --> 00:01:55.670
being in a big crowd like that. Our

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:57.030
little church that we have there in

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:59.190
Collinsville only has

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.870
probably four or five

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:00.880
hundred

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:03.190
people there on a Sunday. But when

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:04.870
you have thousands of people in an

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:06.630
auditorium, it's a big

00:02:06.630 --> 00:02:06.640
difference

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:09.430
for us. But it was so nice

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:11.750
to meet you all. And I want to say, if

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:13.910
you're there, I know it's

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:15.270
exciting to see us, but I want to tell

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:17.110
you, we're just Brandon and Diana.

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:19.430
We appreciate all the honor, and

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.110
we pray for every single one of you if

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:23.190
you want prayer. But like I said, there

00:02:23.190 --> 00:02:23.200
were

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:25.350
so many people at one

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:27.589
time, I told her, "I don't know

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:29.270
how to do that next

00:02:29.270 --> 00:02:29.280
time,"trying

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.190
to go through everything. But

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:32.949
if you came out there and we prayed

00:02:32.959 --> 00:02:34.790
for you, where I'm going

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:37.030
with that is: if you got prayer and

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:40.390
you were in that service,

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:43.350
did you receive your healing?

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:45.670
I'm excited to hear, because there were

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:47.350
some people that had strokes, folks. And

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:48.229
there were some people

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:50.630
battling depression and all kinds of

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:51.910
different things that they were going

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:54.150
through that they needed a miracle. They

00:02:54.160 --> 00:02:56.869
needed a breakthrough in their life.

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:59.509
It was exciting to see them. I'm

00:02:59.519 --> 00:03:00.790
believing that they got touched.

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:02.710
There was one lady,

00:03:02.720 --> 00:03:05.430
folks, who got

00:03:05.430 --> 00:03:05.440
touched

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:07.110
so much that she could hardly drive

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.869
home, and she was supposed to help

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:10.790
navigate her husband clear back to

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:13.270
Austin, Texas. And she didn't

00:03:13.270 --> 00:03:13.280
know—she

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:15.270
was like she was on another

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:18.149
planet. I'm talking

00:03:18.149 --> 00:03:18.159
about,

00:03:18.159 --> 00:03:20.390
she had the Holy Ghost all over her.

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:22.070
It was amazing, wasn't it?

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:22.470
Yeah.

00:03:22.470 --> 00:03:22.480
And

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:24.630
really nice people from

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.949
Estonia. Is that right?

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:29.030
Estonia. Braden

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:31.190
remembers. But

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:32.630
like I said, there were people coming

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:34.149
from everywhere. But I just wanted to

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:36.470
say thank you all, always, for being so

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:38.229
kind. To the people from Houston I met

00:03:38.229 --> 00:03:38.239
who

00:03:38.239 --> 00:03:40.630
had an air duct system business,

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:42.710
they're such a blessing, and we

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:44.869
pray over them and so many people. We

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:47.670
met the people with the dogs, you know,

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:49.509
so it was really interesting.

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:52.229
It's kind of like our public

00:03:52.239 --> 00:03:55.190
debut in a sense, since the ministry is

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:57.589
really growing, to go out and meet

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:58.869
everybody. But I want to keep kicking

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:00.630
that down the road. I mean, we

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.550
can go over things, but one of the

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.630
things is really cool. Now,

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:07.589
I have to go

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:10.949
back. Let me back it up a little bit. As

00:04:10.959 --> 00:04:12.470
we were sitting in the back—because the

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:14.470
Lord told me, before all this

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:16.710
happened, on Wednesday before

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:18.789
we left,

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:21.670
I was overcoming big time and I

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.350
was under attack. I didn't feel good at

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:25.189
all. And I told D, "I

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:27.990
feel too sick to go. I don't feel

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:30.710
like we should go."And she said, "Okay,

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:31.990
well, whatever you want to do,

00:04:31.990 --> 00:04:32.000
babe,"like

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.430
she always is—she's always so

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:35.670
supportive. And I told her, I said,

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.430
"Let's pray."And the Lord said,

00:04:37.430 --> 00:04:37.440
"Brandon,

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:41.030
it's a healing service.

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:43.430
Go expect your miracle."And I said,

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:46.870
"Yeah, well, duh. We'll

00:04:46.870 --> 00:04:46.880
go."And

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.590
so I went and I drove. It

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:51.670
was a long drive. And I told her, I

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:53.670
said, "I'm overcoming so bad right now.

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.710
I'm going to have to pull over to the side

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.950
of the road."And so I

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:58.469
just kept driving by faith. I kept

00:04:58.479 --> 00:04:59.830
standing, I kept quoting the word, I

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:01.189
kept believing, just like I teach you

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:03.510
all. I was

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:05.670
practicing what I preach. And I got

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:08.870
there expecting, but the first night I did

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.870
not feel the presence of the Lord as

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:13.270
strong as what I was wanting, you know,

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:15.110
and I'm not disappointed. It's not Billy Burke's

00:05:15.120 --> 00:05:16.230
fault.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.070
No, it's my

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:19.510
receptor, where I was at.

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:21.670
I'm going into the atmosphere, and it

00:05:21.670 --> 00:05:21.680
wasn't—you

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:23.670
know. So

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:25.830
the Lord said, "Brandon, I want you to

00:05:25.830 --> 00:05:25.840
fast."And

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:27.670
I said, "You want me to

00:05:27.670 --> 00:05:27.680
fast?"I

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:30.870
said, "Okay, for how long?""Until

00:05:30.870 --> 00:05:30.880
that night."I

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:34.070
said, "Well,

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:35.749
that's great. Okay, well, I'll do

00:05:35.749 --> 00:05:35.759
it."So

00:05:35.759 --> 00:05:37.990
I started praying, I started fasting,

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:41.510
and the next morning, I woke up and

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:43.189
I went to the service,

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:46.870
and the glory came on me,

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:49.909
and I felt the power of God hit me.

00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:51.990
I'm telling you, I started

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.670
feeling all the symptoms start lifting

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.270
off of me. I started feeling completely

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:57.189
healed. And I'm telling you, folks,

00:05:57.199 --> 00:06:00.230
the night before,

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:03.270
it was like you could feel it in

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:05.830
the atmosphere, and I was hearing it in

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:07.350
the spirit realm. I don't know if

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:09.430
this was something new for me. I told

00:06:09.440 --> 00:06:10.950
Diana, "This is like

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:12.629
something because I'm listening, but I

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:14.309
can hear things and what the Lord's

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:18.230
showing me. Is this fake?

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.590
This is real. This is what I'm

00:06:19.590 --> 00:06:19.600
hearing."And

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:23.510
you know me, I am so

00:06:23.520 --> 00:06:27.189
huge on miracles and the glory and

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:29.270
the manifestation of everything. But I was

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:30.950
hearing in the atmosphere the

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:32.469
thoughts of—I don't know if it's other

00:06:32.479 --> 00:06:36.070
people around me or what—"Is this fake?

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:39.110
Is this made up? Is this

00:06:39.110 --> 00:06:39.120
performance?"And

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:41.430
it was bombarding my thoughts. And

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:43.270
the Lord said, "Take authority over the

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:45.590
atmosphere."And

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:48.230
I thought, "That's interesting. What

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.390
are you showing me?"Because you know me,

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:53.110
I'm always a student. Diana and I

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.550
are always students. We don't have

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:56.390
everything figured out, but we

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:58.390
want to learn. And I told her,

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:00.629
as we're listening and we're

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:02.309
hearing, what are we

00:07:02.319 --> 00:07:04.309
hearing in the spiritual atmosphere

00:07:04.319 --> 00:07:06.469
of this auditorium right now? And I was

00:07:06.479 --> 00:07:08.790
hearing, "Is this fake? Is this

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:11.270
performance? Is this

00:07:11.270 --> 00:07:11.280
authentic?"All

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:12.710
these things. And it was coming, and

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:15.430
I personally know this man. And

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:17.670
I'm like, "Of course it is."And I started

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:19.510
coming against that, and I was like, "That

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:21.830
is demonic,"but it was coming against

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:24.469
your thoughts. And as I'm standing in

00:07:24.479 --> 00:07:25.589
the back, and that's when I went

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:27.909
into the next day and it was still

00:07:27.919 --> 00:07:29.110
lingering. That's when the Lord told me,

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:31.270
"I want you to fast and pray over

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:32.629
this

00:07:32.629 --> 00:07:32.639
atmosphere."Well,

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:36.230
I went in, and

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:38.469
we drove around like we do all the

00:07:38.479 --> 00:07:40.870
time here in Tulsa, driving around

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:43.029
our area praying. Well, I drove around

00:07:43.039 --> 00:07:45.110
Fort Worth for about seven

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:48.230
hours after the service.

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:49.830
My goodness, they've got

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:52.309
a lot of work to do. I'm not used to a

00:07:52.319 --> 00:07:53.670
major city like that. Sitting

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:56.309
in traffic is like going to Tampa, but we

00:07:56.309 --> 00:07:56.319
were

00:07:56.319 --> 00:07:58.790
just praying over Fort Worth as

00:07:58.790 --> 00:07:58.800
we went

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:00.230
through there, interceding

00:08:00.230 --> 00:08:00.240
and

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:01.670
praying for the glory to come on that

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:03.430
city, praying for a major harvest of

00:08:03.440 --> 00:08:05.589
souls in

00:08:05.589 --> 00:08:05.599
the really

00:08:05.599 --> 00:08:07.430
rough areas.

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:11.909
Well, as we did that, I

00:08:11.919 --> 00:08:13.909
started feeling the atmosphere change

00:08:13.919 --> 00:08:16.309
and was just praying for that meeting

00:08:16.319 --> 00:08:17.990
that night. When we got to the

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:20.950
meeting that night, it was

00:08:20.960 --> 00:08:22.869
packed. But we sat in the back because

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:24.309
the Lord said, 'I want you to sit in the

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:25.990
back and pray over this

00:08:25.990 --> 00:08:26.000
service.'So,

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:28.390
we sat towards the back,

00:08:28.390 --> 00:08:28.400
and

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:31.350
Diana

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:32.790
and I were just interceding. We

00:08:32.790 --> 00:08:32.800
started

00:08:32.800 --> 00:08:34.790
praying,

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:37.269
and you could feel the tangible presence

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:41.990
of God; it was so heavy.

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.829
Both of us, at

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:56.150
the exact same time, felt a crown,

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:59.750
like a glory, come over our heads at the exact same time. I looked at her and said, 'I just felt like a helmet of glory

00:08:59.760 --> 00:09:02.949
came on

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:09.910
my head.'And she said, 'Brandon,

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:11.910
I felt it

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:12.710
too.'It

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:15.190
was amazing, and I felt the glory.

00:09:15.190 --> 00:09:15.200
While

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.710
I was in the

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:19.110
back, the Lord said, 'Receive your

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:21.590
healing. You don't have to have anybody

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.389
touch you. Practice what you preach.'There

00:09:24.389 --> 00:09:24.399
are

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:25.829
so

00:09:25.839 --> 00:09:26.870
many people who think you have to

00:09:26.870 --> 00:09:26.880
have someone

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:28.310
lay hands on you to receive.

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:30.949
No. When you're in the atmosphere of

00:09:30.959 --> 00:09:34.230
glory, and the presence of the Lord is

00:09:34.230 --> 00:09:34.240
there,

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:36.630
receive what you're

00:09:36.640 --> 00:09:38.310
believing for. And the Lord said,

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:41.910
'Believe big. Believe big.'Even if

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:43.509
you're in a service like that and everyone

00:09:43.509 --> 00:09:43.519
else is

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:45.269
getting prayed for, and

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:46.630
you feel like you're the only one

00:09:46.630 --> 00:09:46.640
who

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:48.550
isn't,

00:09:48.560 --> 00:09:51.670
believe God for big things right where you're at. I'm

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:53.590
telling you, it's time to believe Him

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.430
for big

00:09:55.430 --> 00:09:55.440
things—exceedingly,

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:57.030
abundantly, above all that

00:09:57.040 --> 00:09:58.710
you dare ask or think.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:00.630
So, I was sitting back, the power of

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:02.550
God came on me, and I was healed.

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:05.750
I'm making this story too long, but

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.990
after that happened,

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:15.269
we were sitting in there and Diana said, 'I can see the mist. I

00:10:15.269 --> 00:10:15.279
can see the mist.'Tell them, babe. Yeah, we were sitting

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:17.829
in the very back, and I could see this

00:10:17.839 --> 00:10:20.630
light mist coming all into the room.

00:10:20.640 --> 00:10:22.230
You know, when you're in that atmosphere

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.310
and sitting in it,

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:26.230
you don't realize it

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:27.750
until it's right on you. I

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:29.190
started looking, and I was like, 'There's

00:10:29.200 --> 00:10:31.750
a haze in here that wasn't here when

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:35.110
we first walked in, right?'And then,

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:36.870
all of a sudden, all

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:40.710
the fire alarms went off.

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:42.710
We have video of it. I told Braden to tape

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:42.720
it—we

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:44.470
can't play it because

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:47.110
he doesn't have it downloaded yet. But as

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:49.350
we could see the mist, the glory,

00:10:49.360 --> 00:10:51.190
the presence of the Lord started

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:53.430
coming in so strong. There was a man

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:55.829
with cerebral

00:10:55.829 --> 00:10:55.839
palsy whose

00:10:55.839 --> 00:10:57.750
hands were all crippled up when

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:59.430
he got up there, and the power of God hit

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:01.350
his hands and they started straightening

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.550
out.

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:04.069
He said, 'I haven't been able to

00:11:04.079 --> 00:11:05.590
ever do

00:11:05.590 --> 00:11:05.600
this.'I'm

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:08.230
telling you,

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:09.670
this guy's faith

00:11:09.680 --> 00:11:13.190
was off the charts.

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:15.750
It melted me because here

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:18.310
he is, severely

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:20.790
handicapped in the natural,

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:24.470
giving God praise for

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:27.430
where he's at in his life.

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:29.590
It made me

00:11:29.590 --> 00:11:29.600
think,

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:32.150
'What do you ever have to complain

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:33.750
about when you see somebody

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:35.350
overcome?'He

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:38.310
was in the midst of his storm,

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:41.030
praising God to the point

00:11:41.030 --> 00:11:41.040
that

00:11:41.040 --> 00:11:42.870
it challenged me.

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:43.670
That was good.

00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:46.470
It was beautiful.

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:47.990
We saw so many other people

00:11:47.990 --> 00:11:48.000
who

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.590
were believing God for a breakthrough,

00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:52.790
or for many different

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:52.800
things—lumps

00:11:52.800 --> 00:11:54.150
in their chests and all kinds of

00:11:54.150 --> 00:11:54.160
things

00:11:54.160 --> 00:11:55.829
get healed—and it was just

00:11:55.839 --> 00:11:58.550
wonderful. But as those fire alarms were

00:11:58.560 --> 00:12:01.430
going off, I

00:12:01.430 --> 00:12:01.440
do

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:03.110
have to make a disclaimer

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:05.509
here: I do not know what caused the fire

00:12:05.519 --> 00:12:07.590
alarms to go off in the service,

00:12:07.590 --> 00:12:07.600
whether

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:09.910
somebody pulled the alarm

00:12:09.920 --> 00:12:13.670
or whatever. But we did know before

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:15.829
it ever went off,

00:12:15.829 --> 00:12:15.839
Diana

00:12:15.839 --> 00:12:17.750
and I both said,

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:19.910
'You can feel the glory;

00:12:19.920 --> 00:12:21.670
it's in the atmosphere. You can see

00:12:21.680 --> 00:12:25.269
a mist or a fog in here.'Later,

00:12:25.269 --> 00:12:25.279
the

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:28.069
fire

00:12:28.069 --> 00:12:28.079
alarms

00:12:28.079 --> 00:12:30.150
started going off all

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:32.069
throughout the building, and it was

00:12:32.079 --> 00:12:36.150
live. I told D,

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.470
'Did the glory smoke just

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:40.470
set off the fire alarm in the church?'I

00:12:40.470 --> 00:12:40.480
think

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:41.590
it did,

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:43.350
but you don't

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:44.870
want to say that because somebody

00:12:44.880 --> 00:12:46.230
could have pulled the alarm.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:49.030
But

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:50.790
between us thousands of people, I want

00:12:50.790 --> 00:12:50.800
to say

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:53.990
it was the glory that set off that

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:56.629
fire alarm. It was just too cool

00:12:56.629 --> 00:12:56.639
because

00:12:56.639 --> 00:12:58.310
I

00:12:58.310 --> 00:12:58.320
didn't

00:12:58.320 --> 00:12:59.350
want to be hyperspiritual

00:12:59.350 --> 00:12:59.360
or

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:01.190
try

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:03.430
to create sensationalism. I just

00:13:03.440 --> 00:13:05.269
know I'm expecting God to do something

00:13:05.279 --> 00:13:09.030
big, aren't you? I'm expecting God to

00:13:09.040 --> 00:13:11.190
show up and show off in this month of

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:13.910
September.

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:15.910
The Lord told me as I was

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.670
sitting there, 'Brandon, what

00:13:17.680 --> 00:13:20.150
you're seeing is a spiritual arsonist.

00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:22.230
Billy Burke is a spiritual arsonist; he goes and

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:25.350
causes fires in these

00:13:25.350 --> 00:13:25.360
services.'And

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:27.829
He said, 'This

00:13:27.839 --> 00:13:29.910
is what I want you to be—a spiritual

00:13:29.920 --> 00:13:31.910
arsonist for the Lord,

00:13:31.910 --> 00:13:31.920
causing

00:13:31.920 --> 00:13:34.949
fires by the Holy Ghost, stirring people

00:13:34.959 --> 00:13:36.710
up, and getting them ready for the soon

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:38.870
return of the Lord Jesus

00:13:38.870 --> 00:13:38.880
Christ.'It's

00:13:38.880 --> 00:13:41.509
time for you to be excited because God

00:13:41.519 --> 00:13:43.750
is about to show up and show off in your

00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:45.910
life, and I want you to believe Him

00:13:45.920 --> 00:13:48.230
for big things tonight. I want you to believe

00:13:48.240 --> 00:13:51.190
Him that what's impossible in your life

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:53.910
will soon become possible.

00:13:53.920 --> 00:13:56.069
I'm just

00:13:56.079 --> 00:13:58.069
believing right now with you for your

00:13:58.079 --> 00:13:59.910
miracle, for your creative miracle,

00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:02.470
whatever you may need in your life. I

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:04.949
told Diana, 'I'm tired of

00:14:04.959 --> 00:14:07.430
always having this attitude

00:14:07.430 --> 00:14:07.440
of,

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:08.870
well, we're just waiting

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:10.790
for it to happen. We're

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:12.470
ready for the

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:15.269
manifestation now.'And Billy Burke said

00:14:15.279 --> 00:14:16.550
something really cool about it.

00:14:16.550 --> 00:14:16.560
Braden,

00:14:16.560 --> 00:14:17.990
tell them what he

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:19.590
said about the

00:14:23.519 --> 00:14:25.509
grocery cart.

00:14:25.519 --> 00:14:27.110
Yeah, the analogy he had was

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:29.350
amazing because he was saying how

00:14:29.360 --> 00:14:31.670
people don't have that bulldog tenacity

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:33.750
about their healing and what Jesus did

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:35.430
for us on the cross. He

00:14:35.430 --> 00:14:35.440
said

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:37.269
whenever you go into a

00:14:37.279 --> 00:14:39.189
grocery store, you put all your groceries

00:14:39.199 --> 00:14:41.110
in that cart. You don't own the

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:42.949
cart, and you don't own the groceries

00:14:42.949 --> 00:14:42.959
yet—you

00:14:42.959 --> 00:14:44.550
haven't even paid for them. But if

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:46.629
somebody walks up and

00:14:46.629 --> 00:14:46.639
tries

00:14:46.639 --> 00:14:47.829
to push your cart away, you're like,

00:14:47.839 --> 00:14:50.230
'Hey, that's mine!'You will fight

00:14:50.240 --> 00:14:52.470
them over that,

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:54.389
but you don't even own it yet. So, that's

00:14:54.399 --> 00:14:55.670
what he was saying: it's not even yours

00:14:55.680 --> 00:14:55.910
yet,

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:57.670
but Jesus

00:14:57.680 --> 00:14:59.590
already paid it all. Since He paid the

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:01.670
price, we should have that same bulldog

00:15:01.680 --> 00:15:03.910
tenacity of faith over our healing.

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.990
I thought it was an amazing

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:06.790
analogy.

00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:08.310
Even when you don't have the full manifestation

00:15:08.310 --> 00:15:08.320
yet—it's

00:15:08.320 --> 00:15:09.670
like you don't have the

00:15:09.680 --> 00:15:11.590
groceries in your house yet, you just

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:12.790
have them in your buggy and you're

00:15:12.800 --> 00:15:14.150
pushing them around—if

00:15:14.150 --> 00:15:14.160
someone came

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:15.750
up and tried to grab

00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:18.150
your bread or your eggs out of that cart,

00:15:18.150 --> 00:15:18.160
you'd

00:15:18.160 --> 00:15:19.910
go, 'Hey, hold on, those are my

00:15:19.910 --> 00:15:19.920
eggs!'You

00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:21.350
haven't

00:15:21.360 --> 00:15:22.790
even purchased them yet,

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:25.590
but you're bold enough to

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:27.430
tell people, 'Those are

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:29.990
my eggs.'Well, I want you to look at your

00:15:29.990 --> 00:15:30.000
healing

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:31.509
the same way.

00:15:31.519 --> 00:15:32.870
That's my healing.

00:15:32.880 --> 00:15:33.350
Yes,

00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:35.990
that's my deliverance. You may not have

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.910
the full manifestation of what you're

00:15:37.920 --> 00:15:39.750
believing God for, ladies and gentlemen,

00:15:39.760 --> 00:15:41.670
but you got to have that. That's mine

00:15:41.680 --> 00:15:43.829
regardless if I'm

00:15:43.839 --> 00:15:45.670
seeing it or walking in the fruit of it.

00:15:45.680 --> 00:15:48.150
What's in my spiritual cart belongs to

00:15:48.160 --> 00:15:50.710
me. I have this, and I'm going to walk in

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:53.189
it because God paid the price. Jesus

00:15:53.199 --> 00:15:55.670
paid the price for you to walk in total

00:15:55.680 --> 00:15:57.829
victory in your life.

00:15:57.839 --> 00:15:59.749
He paid the price. Nothing's too big,

00:15:59.759 --> 00:16:01.910
and nothing's too small. Jesus paid the

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:04.710
price for you to have it all. And we

00:16:04.720 --> 00:16:06.790
allow the enemy to come in and try to

00:16:06.800 --> 00:16:09.030
rob us, even like what I was doing on

00:16:09.040 --> 00:16:11.670
Wednesday. Yeah, I don't want to

00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:13.829
go to the healing service. I'm overcoming.

00:16:13.839 --> 00:16:16.230
It's a healing service. And I was like,

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:19.030
'You know, okay, believe God in the

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:21.590
healing service.'And so we went. And so,

00:16:21.600 --> 00:16:27.269
you know, it's just trying to

00:16:27.279 --> 00:16:28.870
go through these things and say, 'You

00:16:28.880 --> 00:16:31.509
know what? We got it. We can

00:16:31.519 --> 00:16:32.870
believe God, too.'Just like this. You

00:16:32.880 --> 00:16:35.350
know what I'm saying?

00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:36.629
What I'm trying to do is

00:16:36.639 --> 00:16:39.110
paint it to you all

00:16:39.110 --> 00:16:39.120
that

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.790
Brandon and Diana are believing just

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:43.030
like you all are. We're just believing

00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:45.189
for stuff just like you all are. And

00:16:45.199 --> 00:16:47.350
when I'm overcoming in my body, and

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:49.269
my flesh wanted to lay in

00:16:49.279 --> 00:16:50.870
bed and feel sorry for myself, the Lord

00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:53.990
said, 'I want you to do this. I want you

00:16:54.000 --> 00:16:56.069
to go by faith. I want you to speak to

00:16:56.069 --> 00:16:56.079
it.'And

00:16:56.079 --> 00:16:57.430
it wasn't something that was

00:16:57.440 --> 00:16:59.189
contagious. I was

00:16:59.189 --> 00:16:59.199
overcoming

00:16:59.199 --> 00:17:00.790
something with my own flesh. And you

00:17:00.800 --> 00:17:01.990
know, it's like, 'Well, thanks a

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:04.069
lot for spreading your bug

00:17:04.069 --> 00:17:04.079
around.'No,

00:17:04.079 --> 00:17:06.150
it wasn't a bug. It wasn't anything like

00:17:06.160 --> 00:17:08.150
that. It was something I was overcoming.

00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:10.150
And so I told Diana, I said, 'Let's do

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.669
this by faith.'And we did it. And I

00:17:11.679 --> 00:17:13.750
got what I was believing for.

00:17:13.760 --> 00:17:15.750
And it's the glory. The

00:17:15.760 --> 00:17:17.110
glory. And I'm telling you,

00:17:17.120 --> 00:17:18.630
we're never looking for a

00:17:18.640 --> 00:17:20.549
person. I'm going to tell you this: it's

00:17:20.559 --> 00:17:23.590
not the person, it's Jesus. And Jesus

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:26.630
shows up. And I believe expectation

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:28.870
brings the manifestation of what you're

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:31.110
believing for. And some people

00:17:31.120 --> 00:17:33.830
get frustrated. They go, 'Oh, you know,

00:17:33.840 --> 00:17:35.350
I don't like the

00:17:35.360 --> 00:17:36.950
way he did this. I don't like the

00:17:36.950 --> 00:17:36.960
way...'I

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:38.390
don't like the way everybody does

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:40.470
everything either, folks, but I'm just

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:42.230
believing in an atmosphere of

00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:45.669
expectation that manifestation is coming.

00:17:45.669 --> 00:17:45.679
I

00:17:45.679 --> 00:17:48.630
don't care what church it is. You know,

00:17:48.640 --> 00:17:50.710
I'm just believing God. I'm

00:17:50.710 --> 00:17:50.720
seeking

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:53.590
Jesus at that point,

00:17:53.590 --> 00:17:53.600
not

00:17:53.600 --> 00:17:55.029
getting distracted. It's like going up,

00:17:55.039 --> 00:17:57.029
and after we felt the cloud

00:17:57.029 --> 00:17:57.039
I think,

00:17:57.039 --> 00:17:59.029
you know, we felt all that glory,

00:17:59.039 --> 00:18:01.990
and we felt the presence of the Lord so

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:04.070
strong. I told her, I said, 'I feel

00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:05.669
like if I

00:18:05.679 --> 00:18:06.950
wouldn't have come, I would have been so

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.549
disappointed.

00:18:08.559 --> 00:18:10.710
I would have been so

00:18:10.710 --> 00:18:10.720
disappointed.'When

00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:13.029
you have your antenna of

00:18:13.039 --> 00:18:17.270
expectation up to believe God... So, and

00:18:17.280 --> 00:18:19.430
the other thing was, remember I

00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:21.990
told you all that we would start to

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:25.750
see major generals start to go home.

00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:28.150
And

00:18:28.160 --> 00:18:30.710
not every single one that goes home is

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:31.590
bad.

00:18:31.600 --> 00:18:32.310
No.

00:18:32.310 --> 00:18:32.320
Some—and

00:18:32.320 --> 00:18:33.669
I'm not going to say any of

00:18:33.679 --> 00:18:35.270
these people are bad, folks,

00:18:35.280 --> 00:18:36.549
no.

00:18:36.549 --> 00:18:36.559
They've—some

00:18:36.559 --> 00:18:38.630
of the people that

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:40.710
I've seen, because they've opened some

00:18:40.720 --> 00:18:44.390
doors, they would go home early. But

00:18:44.400 --> 00:18:45.990
that doesn't make you a bad person. That

00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:47.990
just makes you human, right? You know,

00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:49.750
people mess up. That's what I'm talking

00:18:49.760 --> 00:18:52.789
about. But in this case, one of—a dear

00:18:52.789 --> 00:18:52.799
sister—she

00:18:52.799 --> 00:18:54.789
went home. I told you,

00:18:54.799 --> 00:18:57.669
a prayer general—I'm talking a major,

00:18:57.679 --> 00:19:01.510
major, huge prayer general—went home

00:19:01.520 --> 00:19:04.310
yesterday. And it went along with

00:19:04.320 --> 00:19:06.310
what the Lord is showing me about the

00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:08.870
elders going home and the young

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:11.510
generation rising up. We have to take

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:14.310
the baton of prayer.

00:19:14.320 --> 00:19:17.029
Everything we do is birthed out of

00:19:17.039 --> 00:19:19.190
prayer in the spirit realm for

00:19:19.190 --> 00:19:19.200
these

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:21.830
last days in this last revival. And

00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:23.350
that's why the Lord called us. He said,

00:19:23.360 --> 00:19:26.549
'Raise up this million men and

00:19:26.559 --> 00:19:29.830
women prayer

00:19:29.830 --> 00:19:29.840
army.'And

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:33.909
our condolences go out to

00:19:33.919 --> 00:19:35.270
Patsy

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:36.150
Cameneti.

00:19:36.160 --> 00:19:36.789
Her—she

00:19:36.799 --> 00:19:38.789
went home to be

00:19:38.799 --> 00:19:40.950
with the Lord, and she was one of Brother

00:19:40.950 --> 00:19:40.960
Hagin's—he

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:43.830
trained

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:45.350
her up, and she did prayer at his

00:19:45.360 --> 00:19:47.909
